14/08/2007
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- The headcount in the BiH Defence Ministry and the armed forces will decline by 1,912 people, BiH Defence Minister Selmo Cikotic confirmed on Sunday (August 12th).
Of that number, 230 people will be reassigned to new jobs in Federation of BiH institutions.
The process of downsizing and restructuring is the result of creating a single army in BiH.
(NTV Hayat - 12/08/07)
